import React from 'react'
  import { MDXTag } from '@mdx-js/tag'
  

const layoutProps = {
  
};
export default class MDXContent extends React.Component {
  constructor(props) {
    super(props)
    this.layout = null
  }
  render() {
    const { components, ...props } = this.props

    return <MDXTag
             name="wrapper"
             
             components={components}><MDXTag name="p" components={components}>{`Hello 👋,  `}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="p" components={components}>{`Welcome to `}<MDXTag name="strong" components={components} parentName="p">{`Dev Book Club 📔 `}</MDXTag>{`  `}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="p" components={components}>{`We constantly need to retrain and reinvent ourselves to embrace new technological changes. What could be better than gaining knowledge by reading books.`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="p" components={components}>{`So, Let's start with our first topic - `}<MDXTag name="strong" components={components} parentName="p">{`Functional Programming with Haskell!`}</MDXTag>{`  `}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="h2" components={components} props={{"id":"learning-haskel"}}>{`Learning Haskel`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="ul" components={components}>
<MDXTag name="li" components={components} parentName="ul"><MDXTag name="a" components={components} parentName="li" props={{"href":"https://gecgithub01.walmart.com/a0k00xa/ca-dev-bookclub/blob/master/docs/functional-programming.md"}}>{`Understanding Functional Programming`}</MDXTag></MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="li" components={components} parentName="ul"><MDXTag name="a" components={components} parentName="li" props={{"href":"https://gecgithub01.walmart.com/a0k00xa/ca-dev-bookclub/blob/master/docs/why-haskell.md"}}>{`What is Haskell?`}</MDXTag></MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="li" components={components} parentName="ul"><MDXTag name="a" components={components} parentName="li" props={{"href":"https://gecgithub01.walmart.com/a0k00xa/ca-dev-bookclub/blob/master/docs/getting-started.md"}}>{`Getting Started`}</MDXTag></MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="li" components={components} parentName="ul"><MDXTag name="a" components={components} parentName="li" props={{"href":"https://gecgithub01.walmart.com/a0k00xa/ca-dev-bookclub/blob/master/docs/number.md"}}>{`Working with Numbers`}</MDXTag></MDXTag>
</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="h2" components={components} props={{"id":"recommended-resources"}}>{`Recommended Resources`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="h3" components={components} props={{"id":"books"}}>{`Books`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="ul" components={components}>
<MDXTag name="li" components={components} parentName="ul"><MDXTag name="a" components={components} parentName="li" props={{"href":"http://www.cs.nott.ac.uk/~pszgmh/pih.html"}}>{`Programming in Haskell`}</MDXTag>{` `}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="li" components={components} parentName="ul"><MDXTag name="a" components={components} parentName="li" props={{"href":"https://www.amazon.ca/Practical-Haskell-World-Guide-Programming/dp/1484244796/ref=asc_df_1484244796/?tag=googleshopc0c-20&linkCode=df0&hvadid=335213572220&hvpos=1o1&hvnetw=g&hvrand=9725894875958210438&hvpone=&hvptwo=&hvqmt=&hvdev=c&hvdvcmdl=&hvlocint=&hvlocphy=9000810&hvtargid=pla-639707752005&psc=1"}}>{`Practical Haskell: A Real World Guide to Programming`}</MDXTag>{` `}</MDXTag>
</MDXTag>
           </MDXTag>
  }
}
